OL,6,FThat's #9.2 billion lower than the
OL,7,F#105.8 billion the Office for Budget
OL,8,FResponsibility (OBR), the government's
OL,9,Findependent forecaster, was predicting
OL,10,Fjust a few months ago.
OL,12,FOn the face of it, this is encouraging
OL,13,Fnews for the chancellor who is
OL,14,Fpreparing to deliver a Budget in two
OL,15,Fweeks time - a Budget he hopes will
OL,16,Frevive both our economic fortunes and
OL,17,Fthe Tories' popularity.
