OL,3,CLatest OBR forecast shows major tax
OL,4,Ccuts in the Budget are 'impossible'
OL,6,FThe chancellor also has the "fiscal
OL,7,Frule" he set himself - to get Public
OL,8,FSector Net Debt falling as a share of
OL,9,FNational Income in five years time -
OL,10,Fwhich, in theory, he needs to stick to.
OL,12,FJeremy Hunt's problem, according to
OL,13,FTreasury sources, is that on Tuesday
OL,14,Fevening the OBR handed him the latest
OL,15,Fiteration of its economic forecast for
OL,16,Fthe UK which made clear he cannot
OL,17,Fpossible do all of the things he wants
OL,18,Fto.
