OL,3,CLatest OBR forecast shows major tax
OL,4,Ccuts in the Budget are 'impossible'
OL,6,FThe OBR's assessment is that gilt
OL,7,Fyields have risen in the last six
OL,8,Fweeks and with them the cost of
OL,9,Fservicing the government's debt.
OL,11,FThe path of inflation in the next few
OL,12,Fyears is also now expected to be lower
OL,13,Fthan the OBR forecast last November -
OL,14,Fthis is clearly good news in one sense
OL,15,Fbut it would mean that the
OL,16,Fgovernment's decision to freeze the
OL,17,Ftax thresholds for Income Tax and
OL,18,FNational Insurance until 2027/28 will
OL,19,F(stealthily) raise less money.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/9
