OL,3,CLatest OBR forecast shows major tax
OL,4,Ccuts in the Budget are 'impossible'
OL,6,FThe chancellor's "fiscal headroom"
OL,7,F(translation: the leeway or buffer he
OL,8,Fhas within his target on debt) is
OL,9,Fapparently "broadly where it was in
OL,10,Fthe Autumn Statement" - ie #13 billion.
OL,12,FAs it stands, "major are impossible,"
OL,13,Fa source who has seen the OBR figures
OL,14,Ftold me.
OL,16,FUndeterred, the chancellor seems
OL,17,Fdetermined to press ahead with a cut
OL,18,Fto either National Insurance or Income
OL,19,FTax ahead of the general election.
