OL,3,CLatest OBR forecast shows major tax
OL,4,Ccuts in the Budget are 'impossible'
OL,6,FAnd if headroom doesn't exist, he is
OL,7,Finclined to create it.
OL,9,FAnd it now looks likely that, on March
OL,10,F6, Hunt will attempt to put more money
OL,11,Fin people's pockets in the run-up to
OL,12,Fthe election by pencilling in further
OL,13,Fcuts to spending on public services
OL,14,Fafter it.
OL,16,FPublic services are already creaking,
OL,17,Fthe existing spending plans for 2025/
OL,18,F26 and beyond already pretty
OL,19,Fimplausible. But that's a headache for
OL,20,Fwhoever forms the next government.
